ith&nbsp;The Deli Papers&nbsp;air fryer wax paper collection. Its not just paper; its a premium, greaseproof, and eco-friendly experience that transforms your food presentation.</span></p>', 'wax-paper-the-deli-paper-1536x998.jpg', 'Untitled-design-17.png', 'Untitled-design-18.png', '', '', '', 'active', '2025-07-26 08:53:04', '2025-07-26 08:53:58', 'yes');
