ent paper comes in pre-cut sheets and customizable rolls to fit every baking tray and mold.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Why Should You Pick Our Parchment Paper?</span></p><p>Baking is an expression of love, and our parchment paper is crafted to honor that sentiment. Our product stands out for its:</p><ol><li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Strength &amp; Non-Stick Surface:</span>&nbsp;Engineered for excellence, our deli parchment paper is durable and greaseproof. It ensures your baked goods slide off effortlessly, leaving no residue behind. Whether youre baking cookies, roasting vegetables, or creating delicate pastries, our parchment paper has you covered.</li><li><br></li><li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Vibrant Bakes:</span>&nbsp;The deli parchment paper makes a statement with bold colors and patterns that stand out. Imagine wrapping a chocolate cake in a vibrant floral print or lining your pie crust with a whimsical design. Its not just about functionality; its about adding joy to your baking process.</li><li><br></li><li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Eco-Conscious Choice:</span>&nbsp;Feel good about giving with our deli parchment paper made from recycled and sustainable sources. When you choose our parchment paper, youre making a small but impactful choice for the environmentone that aligns with your love for baking and the planet.</li><li><br></li><li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Wrap in Style:</span>&nbsp;The deli parchment paper is not just for wrapping gifts; its for creating memories. Wrap your baked goods with love and a touch of artistry with our exquisite parchment paper. Whether its a birthday, wedding, holiday, or just because, our parchment paper is the perfect finishing touch to show how much you care.</li></ol><p><br></p>', 'Parchment-paper-the-deli-paper-1536x998.jpg', 'Untitled-design-26.png', 'Untitled-design-19.png', '', '', '', 'active', '2025-07-26 09:33:54', '2025-07-26 09:33:54', 'yes');
INSERT INTO `product` (`product_id`, `product_name`, `product_url`, `product_short_description`, `product_content`, `product_thumbnail`, `product_image1`, `product_image2`, `product_meta_title`, `product_meta_description`, `product_meta_keywords`, `product_status`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `product_index`) VALUES ('12', 'Paper Bags', 'paper-bags', 'From boutiques to bakeries, these The Deli Paper bags serve as walking billboards, subtly promoting businesses while carrying our purchases. So, whether youre a business owner seeking packaging solutions, a conscious consumer, or someone with a penchant for upcycling, lets explore the folds of The Deli Paper bags together.', '<ol><li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Environmentally Responsible Production</span></li></ol><p>Crafted from renewable resources, our&nbsp;paper bags&nbsp;help reduce reliance on single-use plastics, contributing to a cleaner planet. Manufactured using sustainable practices, ensuring minimal environmental footprint throughout the production process.</p><ol><li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Robust and Reliable Construction</span></li></ol><p>Engineered with&nbsp;<a href=\"https://thedelipaper.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">high-quality paper</a>&nbsp;materials, our&nbsp;paper bags&nbsp;are designed to withstand the rigors of everyday use, offering exceptional strength and durability. Reinforced handles provide added support, making these&nbsp;paper bags&nbsp;ideal for carrying groceries, merchandise, or personal belongings with ease.</p><ol><li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Versatile Usage for Various Applications</span></li></ol><p>From retail shopping to event giveaways, these versatile&nbsp;paper bags&nbsp;are suitable for a wide range of purposes, catering to both business and personal needs. Perfect for packaging goods, organizing items, or presenting gifts in an eco-friendly and stylish manner.</p><ol><li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Customizable Options for Branding</span></li></ol><p>Elevate your brand presence with custom printing or branding options available for our&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">paper bags</span>. Personalize each bag with your logo, slogan, or artwork to enhance brand recognition and create a lasting impression on customers.</p><ol><li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Biodegradable and Recyclable</span></li></ol><p>After use, our&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">paper bags</span>&nbsp;can be easily recycled or composted, minimizing waste and promoting a circular economy. Biodegradable materials ensure that even if disposed of improperly, these&nbsp;paper bags&nbsp;will naturally break down over time, leaving no harmful residue behind.</p>', 'Paper-Bags_The_deli_paper-1-1536x998.jpg', '', '', '', '', '', 'active', '2025-07-26 09:41:12', '2025-07-26 09:41:12', 'yes');
